name: Sleeves - Your size
description:
If our sleeves donÂ´t fit your laptop, we will be happy to customize a sleeve especially for you.

This is what we need from you:

1. The size of your laptop in cm (height x width x depth)
2. Your choice of model (see collection)
3. If you have any specific wishes regarding materials we will try our utmost to fulfill them. 

Email this information to mail@justncase.dk and we will get back to you as soon as possible.

Prices from Euro 149.-

Please note the delivery time is 1-2 weeks and it is NOT POSSIBLE to return customized or specially designed sleeves.
